 ____________ &lt;---- *out &lsqb;we calculate that&rsqb;
|flags       |             /|&bsol;
|task *--&gt;   |              |
|task_list   |&lt;----    list_entry
|  prev * --&gt;|    |         |
|  next * --&gt;|    |         |
